it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.visitors.impl
Class AbstractEcolawVisitor

java.lang.Object
  it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.visitors.impl.AbstractEcolawVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
EcolawVisitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
VarRetrieverVisitor
public abstract class AbstractEcolawVisitor
extends Object
implements EcolawVisitor

This abstract class provides basic eco-law navigation capabailities, commonly used while visiting.

Some methods are provided in order to allow the insertion of custom behaviours.

Author:
Paolo Contessi
